 Yuzhong''']]}}\n{{Image label|x=605|y=370|scale=890/890|text=[[Dadukou District|'''2. Dadukou''']]}}\n{{Image label|x=605|y=390|scale=890/890|text=[[Jiangbei District, Chongqing|'''3. Jiangbei''']]}}\n{{Image label|x=605|y=410|scale=890/890|text=[[Shapingba District|'''4. Shapingba''']]}}\n{{Image label|x=605|y=430|scale=890/890|text=[[Jiulongpo District|'''5. Jiulongpo''']]}}\n{{Image label|x=605|y=450|scale=890/890|text=[[Nan'an District|'''6. Nan'an''']]}}\n{{Image label end}}\n</div>\n|-\n!! scope=\"col\" rowspan=2 | [[Administrative division codes of the People's Republic of China|Division code]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.stats.gov.cn/tjbz/cxfldm/2011/index.html |script-title=zh:\u56fd\u5bb6\u7edf\u8ba1\u5c40\u7edf\u8ba1\u7528\u533a\u5212\u4ee3\u7801 |publisher=National Bureau of Statistics of the People's Republic of China |language=zh-hans  |access-date=9 December 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130405092331/http://www.stats.gov.cn/tjbz/cxfldm/2011/index.html |archive-date=5 April 2013 |url-status=dead |df=dmy-all }}</ref>\n!! scope=\"col\" rowspan=2 | Division\n!! scope=\"col\" rowspan=2 | Area in km<sup>2</sup><ref>{{lang|zh-hans|\u300a\u4fdd\u5b9a\u7ecf\u6d4e\u7edf\u8ba1\u5e74\u92742011\u300b}}</ref>{{full citation needed|date=May 2019}}\n!! scope=\"col\" rowspan=2 |Total population 2010<ref>{{cite book <!--|editor1 =Census Office of the State Council of the People's Republic of China |editor2 = Population and Employment Statistics Division of the National Bureau of Statistics of the People's Republic of China --> |script-title=zh:\u4e2d\u56fd2010\u5e74\u4eba\u53e3\u666e\u67e5\u5206\u4e61\u3001\u9547\u3001\u8857\u9053\u8d44\u6599 |year = 2012 |publisher=China Statistics Print |location=Beijing |isbn=978-7-5037-6660-2 |edition = 1st }}<!--|accessdate=25 November 2015--></ref>\n!! scope=\"col\" rowspan=2 |Urban area<br />population 2010<ref name=\"2010PRCcensus\">{{cite book |editor= \u56fd\u52a1\u9662\u4eba\u53e3\u666e\u67e5\u529e\u516